    "body": "Okay, my bad. It was happening because I wasn't properly cleaning up. Instead of running `make devnet-clean` I was just removing all docker volumes. I think some data is saved to bind mounts instead of volumes, so every time I was upping the environment thinking that it was from genesis, there was actually a lot of importing taking place (stuff from previous runs), which was delaying everything else. With proper cleaning it works as expected.",
